data.title: Denain
data.description: Nature line lanyard made in resistant 100% cotton. Round accessory for customization and neck safety closure made of wheat straw, with metal swivel carabiner.  Wheat straw promotes the use of natural raw materials, reducing pollutant emissions.

data.title: Loriet
data.description: Nature line lanyard made of resistant 300D RPET polyester, with metal swivel hook. Label with RPET distinctive and available in a wide range of colours, white special for sublimation.  The RPET material is made from recycled plastic, promoting the reuse of plastic waste and helping the sustainability of the planet.

data.title: Trimax
data.description: Cool lanyard for smartphone made of resistant polyester. With carrying accessory to place between the case and the smartphone and a metal swivel carabiner. Neck adjuster and lanyard tips in chrome finish. Available in a wide range of colours.

data.title: Nerthus
data.description: Nature line lanyard made of resistant recycled cardboard. With metal swivel carabiner.

data.title: Tures
data.description: Nature line identifier made of resistant recycled cardboard. With triple die-cutting and 8,5x3 cm window.

data.title: Binem
data.description: Recycled cardboard identifier. Including card with wildflower seeds, thus converting it into planting paper at the end of its lifespan. Wildflowers in assorted colours, with planting instructions inside and Made in Europe emblem.

data.title: Maes
data.description: Identifier in PVC with matching color lanyard in bright tones and with carabiner closure. Circular tablet for printing.

data.title: Bindel
data.description: Colorful aluminum name tag and rear hook clip for secure accessory.

data.title: Sigex
data.description: Lanyard in resistant and soft silicone in a varied range of vivid colors. With carabiner accessory and strap with buckle closure. With central pad for printing.

data.title: Briol
data.description: Lanyard in resistant and soft polyester in varied colors, detachable with buckle closure. With metallic carabiner accessory and strap with buckle closure.

data.title: Solip
data.description: Name tag embossed in PVC with fixing clip in white. Available in horizontal and vertical design.

data.title: Bizzot
data.description: Identifier stamped in PVC in vertical design.

data.title: Alter
data.description: Identifier stamped in PVC with header in varied colors, transparent front window and back in white.

data.title: Tremen
data.description: Original lanyard in resistant polyester in bicolor design and bright tones with metallic carabiner closure.

data.title: Cail
data.description: Identifier stamped in PVC with lanyard and metallic carabiner closures in varied colors.

data.title: Itaka
data.description: Practical and comfortable silicone lanyard in bold colors with built-in smartphone holder. With adjustable accessory and carabiner closure.

data.title: Perux
data.description: Lanyard in resistant and soft polyester string in a varied range of bright tones. With detachable snap closure on collar, metal carabiner accessory and central pad for printing.

data.title: Upsin
data.description: Name tag in shiny finishing. Rear side with double fixing system - metal clips and safety pin- for secure adjustment.

data.title: Venkal
data.description: Name tag with aluminum frames in anodized finish. Rear side with hooking clip for secure accessory.

data.title: Veltux
data.description: Practical and comfortable silicone lanyard in bold colors with built-in smartphone holder and card pocket. With adjustable accessory and carabiner closure.

data.title: Nopak
data.description: Lanyard with special wide strips in resistant and soft polyester with metallic carabiner accessory. Especially designed for total customization in sublimation. Orders from 250 pieces.

data.title: Kappin
data.description: Lanyard in resistant polyester, with neck security accessory and metal carabiner. Available in a wide range of vivid colors.

data.title: Kunel
data.description: Ready to organize or sponsor an important conference? What more ideal than to gift a beautiful lanyard to hold employees and guests credentials. Reusable and with a modern touch of vivid colours in its cord, its made with resistant polyester and has a multifunction buckle closure and metal hook.

data.title: Lemer
data.description: Handy polyester lanyard with retractable accessory. Security neck closure and extensible accessory with clip in one side, leaving the other side blank for logo. Metal carabiner. Set available in white and black colors.

data.title: Mirok
data.description: Nature line lanyard in 100% cotton material. Natural color and including a metal carabiner.

data.title: Bosur
data.description: Extendable ID holder in a sober design, with hook accessory for ID and an extendable mechanism of up to 65 cm length. With metal carabiner and a wide printing area.

data.title: Napper
data.description: Extendable ID holder in a sober design, with button closure accessory for ID and an extendable mechanism of up to 75 cm length. With metal carabiner and a wide printing area.

data.title: Troix
data.description: Lanyard of nature line in 100% cotton material. Buckle and neck safety lock in wheat straw/PP, to encourage the use of natural raw materials and reduce pollutant emissions. With metallic rotating carabiner and available in natural colour.

data.title: Bespal
data.description: Lanyard of nature line in natural cork. Buckle and neck safety lock in wheat straw/PP, to encourage the use of natural raw materials and reduce pollutant emissions. With metallic rotating carabiner and available in natural colour.

data.title: Neck
data.description: Original lanyard in resistant polyester in bright tones with metallic carabiner closure.

data.title: Duble
data.description: Lanyard in resistant and soft polyester in varied colors. With metallic carabiner accessory.

data.title: Ifem
data.description: Identifier stamped in PVC in horizontal design.

data.title: Sartal
data.description: Nature line identifier made of natural cork, promoting the use of natural raw materials and reducing pollutant emissions. Security fastening, with safety pin at the back side.

data.title: Yest
data.description: Antibacterial lanyard in white polyester with metal carabiner.   Products with antibacterial treatments are able to drastically reduce the bacterial loads present on the surfaces of the materials, thanks to the incorporation of permanent static microbial agents, with high effectiveness in inhibiting and preventing bacterial contamination.  Article according to the ISO 22196 standard, which determines the antibacterial activity in plastic materials and non-porous surfaces, which allows us to know the effectiveness of microbial inhibition that the additives have on the treated objects by means of a quantitative evaluation.

data.title: Merul
data.description: Nature line lanyard made of natural cork with a tubular finish. With safety neck zip in wheat straw/PP and metal carabiner. Includes central cork area for printing.

data.title: Bob
data.description: Lanyard in resistant and soft polyester in varied colors with waterproof cap. Detachable, with buckle closures, metal carabiner and strap.
